<title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="lec-VVVVVV" text="title"/></title>

<statement>
  <p>Escoge una fracción que puedas comparar con <m>\frac{3}{8}</m> y con <m>\frac{5}{6}</m> al examinar los numeradores y los denominadores.</p>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[++++++++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p>Sample response: <m>\frac{3}{6}</m> is greater than <m>\frac{3}{8}</m> because there are 3 parts but the parts are bigger since sixths are bigger than eighths. <m>\frac{3}{6}</m> is less than <m>\frac{5}{6}</m> because it has 2 fewer sixths.</p>
</solution>

</exercise>
